svg.text: 1,609 job ads matched to 3,150 candidates in Richmond, VA
Match scores between job ads and candidates: Critical Care Nurses in Richmond, VA
Percent of Resumes In Match Group
Each vertical line is one job ad (sorted by median match score, low to high)
Each vertical line is one job. The colored segments within each line show how many candidates matched to that job at a certain level.
10% of candidates had a strong match to this job (67-100% of requested skills)
20% of candidates had a medium match to this job (34-66% of requested skills)
45% of candidates had a weak match to this job (1-33% of requested skills)
25% of candidates had no match to this job (none of the requested skills)
